      <title>印度采取措施吸引更多资金流入以阻止卢比贬值</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/india-takes-steps-to-attract-more-inflows-to-stem-rupee-decline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度央行表示，将允许银行提高向非印度居民提供的利率，以吸引更多资金流入，阻止卢比贬值。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/india-takes-steps-to-attract-more-inflows-to-stem-rupee-decline</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 05:17:45 GMT</pubDate>
